==教練生涯==
2009年7月，賀斯菲特成為[[維爾港足球會|維爾港]]的球員兼助教，一年後他獲球會提供一份全職助教的合約。時任維爾港領隊{{Link-en|米奇·亞當斯|Micky Adams}}強調他在2010/11球季會有較沉重的工作量，並且要制訂一份球員目錄和了解所有各級別的聯賽<ref name="help" />。然而，米奇·亞當斯亦說道他或許仍然會被註冊成為球員，以備不時之需<ref name="help">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/p/port_vale/8742199.stm|title=Port Vale boss Micky Adams wants Geoff Horsfield help|date=24 June 2010|work=BBC Sport|accessdate=24 June 2010}}</ref>，這意味著他將要花大量時間去摸索這些球隊<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.thisisstaffordshire.co.uk/news/Port-Vale-Horsfield-s-number-focus-number-s-job/article-2456723-detail/article.html|title=Port Vale: Horsfield's number one focus now on his number two's job|last=Shaw|first=Steve|date=27 July 2010|work=The Sentinel|accessdate=27 July 2010|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130505150855/http://www.thisisstaffordshire.co.uk/Port-Vale-Horsfield-s-number-focus-number-s-job/story-12495500-detail/story.html%23axzz2SQnH3oVi|archivedate=2013年5月5日}}</ref>。

2010年12月，隨著米奇·亞當斯離任領隊一職，賀斯菲特與{{Link-en|馬克·格魯|Mark Grew}}成為維爾港的[[看守領隊|看守領隊]]<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.port-vale.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10381~2254349,00.html |title=MICKY LEAVES VALE |date=30 December 2010 |work=port-vale.co.uk |accessdate=30 December 2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120306063453/http://www.port-vale.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0%2C%2C10381~2254349%2C00.html |archivedate=2012-03-06 }}</ref>。在他們的指揮下，維爾港首場賽事便以0-5的比分不敵[[洛達咸足球會|洛達咸]]<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_3/9310490.stm|title=Rotherham   5 - 0   Port Vale|date=1 January 2011|work=BBC Sport|accessdate=6 January 2011}}</ref>，但是在第二場則聯手帶領球隊以2-1的比分擊敗[[伯顿足球俱乐部|伯顿]]<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_3/9313720.stm|title=Port Vale   2 - 1   Burton Albion|date=3 January 2011|work=BBC Sport|accessdate=6 January 2011}}</ref>。隨著{{Link-en|吉姆·甘農|Jim Gannon}}獲任命為領隊後<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/p/port_vale/9343059.stm|title=Port Vale appoint Jim Gannon as new manager|date=6 January 2011|work=BBC Sport|accessdate=6 January 2011|archive-date=2011-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110106075639/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/port_vale/9343059.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他亦獲留任助教一職<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.thisisstaffordshire.co.uk/news/Port-Vale-Gannon-pleased-inherit-backroom-staff/article-3074448-detail/article.html|title=Port Vale: Gannon pleased to inherit backroom staff|date=7 January 2011|work=The Sentinel|accessdate=7 January 2011}}</ref>。但吉姆·甘農於上任後僅74日後便因成績不濟而遭革職，賀斯菲特與馬克·格魯再次負責暫代職務<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/port_vale/9431553.stm |title=Manager Jim Gannon parts company with Port Vale |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-03-21 |accessdate=2011-03-22 |archive-date=2011-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110323234509/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/port_vale/9431553.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

